---
// src/pages/privacy.astro
import PublicLayout from "@/layouts/PublicLayout.astro";

const lastUpdated = "April 2026";
---

<PublicLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — Hidden Gems Boise"
  description="Privacy Policy for Hidden Gems Boise."
>
  <div class="legal-layout section-container">
    <div class="legal-header">
      <h1 class="legal-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="legal-updated">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-body">
      <p class="legal-intro">
        Your privacy matters to us. This policy explains what information we
        collect, how we use it, and the choices you have.
      </p>

      <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>We collect information in the following ways:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Business submissions:</strong> Name, email, phone, business details,
          and billing information provided when submitting or claiming a listing
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Account information:</strong> Email and name when you create a business
          owner account
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Reviews and comments:</strong> Name, email, and content submitted
          through reviews or event comments
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Usage data:</strong> Standard web analytics including pages visited,
          time on site, and referring URLs
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Cookies:</strong> Session cookies for authentication and analytics
          cookies to understand usage patterns
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Review and approve business listings and claims</li>
        <li>Communicate with business owners about their listings</li>
        <li>Process subscription payments</li>
        <li>Display reviews and comments on listing pages</li>
        <li>Improve the Directory and understand how it is used</li>
        <li>Send transactional emails related to your account or listing</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>3. Information Sharing</h2>
      <p>
        We do not sell your personal information. We may share information with:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Payment processors:</strong> To handle subscription billing securely
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Service providers:</strong> Third-party tools that help us operate
          the Directory (hosting, email, analytics)
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Legal requirements:</strong> When required by law or to protect
          our rights
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. Business Listing Information</h2>
      <p>
        Information you provide for your public listing (business name, address,
        phone, website, photos, bio) will be publicly visible on the Directory.
        Owner information (your name and email) is kept private and not
        displayed publicly.
      </p>

      <h2>5. Reviews and User Content</h2>
      <p>
        Reviews submitted to the Directory display the reviewer's name. Email
        addresses provided with reviews are used only for verification and
        moderation purposes and are not displayed publicly.
      </p>

      <h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
      <p>
        We retain account and listing data for as long as your account is
        active. If you delete your account or your listing is removed, we may
        retain certain information as required by law or for legitimate business
        purposes.
      </p>

      <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Access the personal information we hold about you</li>
        <li>Request correction of inaccurate information</li>
        <li>
          Request deletion of your information (subject to legal requirements)
        </li>
        <li>Opt out of non-transactional communications</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        To exercise these rights, contact us at <a
          href="mailto:hello@hiddengemsboise.com">hello@hiddengemsboise.com</a
        >.
      </p>

      <h2>8. Security</h2>
      <p>
        We take reasonable measures to protect your information from
        unauthorized access, disclosure, or loss. However, no internet
        transmission is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute
        security.
      </p>

      <h2>9. Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        We use essential cookies for authentication and session management. We
        may also use analytics cookies to understand how visitors use the
        Directory. You can control cookies through your browser settings, though
        disabling certain cookies may affect functionality.
      </p>

      <h2>10. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        The Directory is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly
        collect personal information from children under 13.
      </p>

      <h2>11. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify
        registered users of material changes by email. Continued use of the
        Directory after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.
      </p>

      <h2>12. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about this Privacy Policy? Contact us at <a
          href="mailto:hello@hiddengemsboise.com">hello@hiddengemsboise.com</a
        >.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</PublicLayout>

<style>
  .legal-layout {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding-top: 4rem;
    padding-bottom: 5rem;
  }
  .legal-header {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-gem-border);
  }
  .legal-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .legal-updated {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-gem-text-subtle);
  }
  .legal-intro {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-gem-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    background: var(--color-gem-mist);
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-gem-gold);
  }
  .legal-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .legal-body h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-gem-text);
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.625rem;
  }
  .legal-body p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-gem-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .legal-body ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.375rem;
  }
  .legal-body li {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-gem-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }
  .legal-body strong {
    color: var(--color-gem-text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .legal-body a {
    color: var(--color-gem-gold);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .legal-body a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
